{"tid":1122203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誘女孩口愛！結果他生孩沒屁眼　法官酌情判3年","createTime":"2019-04-23T21:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T07:42:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"09e0c024b0a436c33241b6dfcea1377787821ffa","tid":1122203,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T21:57:18.000Z","msg":"新加坡一名12歲少女與一名已婚的緬甸籍男子觀看球賽時，突然好奇詢問「睪丸被球打到會痛嗎？」隨即被反問「妳有口交經驗嗎？」男子竟一時性起解開沙籠裙，要求少女替他進行口交。少女事發後兩年才到警局報案，法官酌情男子事發後與妻子生下的小孩沒有肛門，必須多次進行手術，因此僅輕判他36個月有期徒刑。<br />\n《中國報》報導，緬甸籍男子和妻子2007年赴新加坡工作，2009年向一名12歲少女的父母租房間居住，他於2015年一日坐在沙發上看球賽，少女隨後坐在一旁一同觀看賽事，期間少女詢問「男人的睪丸被球打到，會感覺疼痛嗎？」他反問少女是否有口交經驗後，再問少女是否願意嘗試口交。<br />\n此時，男子一時性起解開沙籠裙，少女則彎下腰替他口交，不久後對方停下動作，他則穿回紗籠裙。直至事發兩年後的2017年，少女才到警察局報案揭發此事。男子的代表律師求情表示，男子在緬甸擁有工程系的大學文憑，在新加坡擔任技術員9年，是第一次犯罪。<br />\n代表律師還提到男子育有一名女兒，但出生時沒有肛門，尿道、子宮、和大小腸則被封在體內，導致尿道發炎必須多次進行手術。男子也向法官請求輕判，讓他回國陪家人度過難關。法官酌情男子的種種因素，輕判他36個月的有期徒刑。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190424/640_668d6a4f84007f407c4ed173d03fd4b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190424%2F640_668d6a4f84007f407c4ed173d03fd4b1.jpg&h=88c1f5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190424/640_4ec0ac41c45f9e61b0240e4874f07b71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190424%2F640_4ec0ac41c45f9e61b0240e4874f07b71.jpg&h=eb7e0327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紗籠裙示意圖，與新聞內容無關。《維基百科》<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190424/1555566/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190424%2F1555566%2F&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=29c22f86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190424%2F1555566%2F&h=8d26a88f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190424/1555566/</a>"},{"pid":"e25ee07f967446b471579c258a4c8ed86e0a9144","tid":1122203,"uid":26035,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報應"},{"pid":"4bb3653fc7cb09b42ff7bac58557542a88617d87","tid":1122203,"uid":241981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:14:31.000Z","msg":"就是一條狗."},{"pid":"6fd32024e3fe49cf3ea0fe28e94ca5eaa2fd8f4f","tid":1122203,"uid":73,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:26:23.000Z","msg":"生女冇屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba07d76ca85db2af05b92b7229975989ef83757","tid":1122203,"uid":8171,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:33:47.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲都可以係求情理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bbad906c2864f058e7cee44b30fefaaaf6da1c","tid":1122203,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e25ee07f967446b471579c258a4c8ed86e0a9144","tid":1122203,"uid":26035,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報應"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a443ce4700a0182fb2710cab05252f99ae06ea13","tid":1122203,"uid":62532,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"bba07d76ca85db2af05b92b7229975989ef83757","tid":1122203,"uid":8171,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:33:47.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲都可以係求情理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:02:52.000Z","msg":"呢個理由VALID過基督徒 捐錢 名校出身好撚多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im